226 (old No.), South Road, at the S.E. corner of 153rd Street, (Jacob Place), showing the Henry Hanna house, of which, Abraham Bergen was the owner in 1860.  This house, which was still standing in 1929, was from 1873-1891, the residence of the first named person.
